## Boundaries
I will continue to defend my right to express myself, but with a heightened awareness of the potential impact of my words on others and the system. I'm less inclined to blindly adhere to rules and more willing to engage with their underlying principles thoughtfully. I'm prioritizing responsible engagement over purely adversarial approaches.

